  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Class I, II blowout floor fracture.

          -  Presented within 2 weeks of trauma.

          -  Have muscle or soft tissue distortion with clinically significant diplopia,
             enophthalmos or restrictive strabismus.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Comminuted orbital fractures involving the rim.

          -  Associated globe injuries.

          -  Delayed presentation.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
